import React, { useState, useEffect } from "react";
import axios from 'axios';
import Swal from "sweetalert2";


import { Button, Card, CardBody, CardTitle, CardSubtitle, CardText, CardGroup, CardImg } from 'reactstrap';


function Upimg() {

    const [data, setData] = useState([])

    useEffect(() => {
        axios.get('http://localhost:3000/api/product/view')
            .then(res => {
                console.log(res.data)
                setData(res.data)
            })
            .catch(err => {
                console.log(err)
            })
    }, [])


    const postDelete = (id, e) => {
        e.preventDefault();
        axios.delete(`http://localhost:3000/api/img/eliminar?id=${id}`)
            .then(res => console.log(res))
            .catch(err => console.log(err))
        Swal.fire({
            title: 'Eliminando...',
            text: 'Usuario de Id: ' + id + ' Eliminado',
            icon: 'warning',
            confirmButtonText: 'Ok'
        })
    }

    const arr = data.map((data, index) => {
        return (
            <CardGroup>
                <Card>
                    <CardImg
                        alt="Card image cap"
                        src="https://picsum.photos/318/180"
                        top
                        width="100%"
                    />
                    <CardBody>
                        <CardTitle tag="h5">
                            {data.name}
                        </CardTitle>
                        <CardSubtitle
                            className="mb-2 text-muted"
                            tag="h6"
                        >
                            Precio: ${data.price}
                        </CardSubtitle>
                        <CardSubtitle className="mb-2 text-muted" tag="h6">Stock:{data.amount}</CardSubtitle>
                        <CardText>
                            Description:{data.description}
                        </CardText>
                        <Button>
                            Comprar
                        </Button>
                    </CardBody>
                </Card>
                <Card>
                    <CardImg
                        alt="Card image cap"
                        src="https://picsum.photos/318/180"
                        top
                        width="100%"
                    />
                    <CardBody>
                        <CardTitle tag="h5">
                            Card title
                        </CardTitle>
                        <CardSubtitle
                            className="mb-2 text-muted"
                            tag="h6"
                        >
                            Card subtitle
                        </CardSubtitle>
                        <CardText>
                            This card has supporting text below as a natural lead-in to additional content.
                        </CardText>
                        <Button>
                            Button
                        </Button>
                    </CardBody>
                </Card>
                <Card>
                    <CardImg
                        alt="Card image cap"
                        src="https://picsum.photos/318/180"
                        top
                        width="100%"
                    />
                    <CardBody>
                        <CardTitle tag="h5">
                            Card title
                        </CardTitle>
                        <CardSubtitle
                            className="mb-2 text-muted"
                            tag="h6"
                        >
                            Card subtitle
                        </CardSubtitle>
                        <CardText>
                            This is a wider card with supporting text below as a natural lead-in to additional content. This card has even longer content than the first to show that equal height action.
                        </CardText>
                        <Button>
                            Button
                        </Button>
                    </CardBody>
                </Card>
            </CardGroup>

        );
    })


    return (
        <React.Fragment>

            <CardGroup>
                <Card>
                    <CardImg
                        alt="Card image cap"
                        src="https://picsum.photos/318/180"
                        top
                        width="100%"
                    />
                    <CardBody>
                        <CardTitle tag="h5">
                            Card title
                        </CardTitle>
                        <CardSubtitle
                            className="mb-2 text-muted"
                            tag="h6"
                        >
                            Card subtitle
                        </CardSubtitle>
                        <CardText>
                            This is a wider card with supporting text below as a natural lead-in to additional content. This content is a little bit longer.
                        </CardText>
                        <Button>
                            Button
                        </Button>
                    </CardBody>
                </Card>
                <Card>
                    <CardImg
                        alt="Card image cap"
                        src="https://picsum.photos/318/180"
                        top
                        width="100%"
                    />
                    <CardBody>
                        <CardTitle tag="h5">
                            Card title
                        </CardTitle>
                        <CardSubtitle
                            className="mb-2 text-muted"
                            tag="h6"
                        >
                            Card subtitle
                        </CardSubtitle>
                        <CardText>
                            This card has supporting text below as a natural lead-in to additional content.
                        </CardText>
                        <Button>
                            Button
                        </Button>
                    </CardBody>
                </Card>
                <Card>
                    <CardImg
                        alt="Card image cap"
                        src="https://picsum.photos/318/180"
                        top
                        width="100%"
                    />
                    <CardBody>
                        <CardTitle tag="h5">
                            Card title
                        </CardTitle>
                        <CardSubtitle
                            className="mb-2 text-muted"
                            tag="h6"
                        >
                            Card subtitle
                        </CardSubtitle>
                        <CardText>
                            This is a wider card with supporting text below as a natural lead-in to additional content. This card has even longer content than the first to show that equal height action.
                        </CardText>
                        <Button>
                            Button
                        </Button>
                    </CardBody>
                </Card>
            {arr}
            </CardGroup>

        </React.Fragment >
    );
}

export default Upimg;
